#: ../../../prop_sf/CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES.rst:2
msgid "CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_sf/CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES.rst:6
msgid ""
"``CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES`` is a boolean specifying whether CMake will scan the "
"source for C++ module dependencies.  See also the :prop_fs:"
"`CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES` file set property which, if set, overrides the per-"
"source settings and the :prop_tgt:`CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES` target property."
msgstr ""
"``CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES`` 是一個布林值，指定 CMake 是否將掃描來源中的 C++ 模組"
"依賴關係。另請參閱 :prop_fs:`CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES` 檔案集屬性，如果設定了該屬"
"性，它會覆寫每個來源的設定和 :prop_tgt:`CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES` 目標屬性。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES.rst:12
msgid ""
"When this property is set ``ON``, CMake will scan the source at build time "
"and add module dependency information to the compile line as necessary.  "
"When this property is set ``OFF``, CMake will not scan the source at build "
"time.  When this property is unset, the :prop_tgt:`CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES` "
"target property is consulted."
msgstr ""
"當此屬性設為 ``ON`` 時，CMake 將在建置時掃描來源並在必要時將模組依賴資訊新增"
"到編譯命令列中。當此屬性設為 ``OFF`` 時，CMake 將不在建置時掃描來源。當此屬性"
"未設定時，將參考 :prop_tgt:`CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES` 目標屬性。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/CXX_SCAN_FOR_MODULES.rst:18
msgid ""
"Note that scanning is only performed if C++20 or higher is enabled for the "
"target and the source uses the ``CXX`` language.  Scanning for modules in "
"sources belonging to file sets of type ``CXX_MODULES`` is always performed."
msgstr ""
"請注意，僅當為目標啟用了 C++20 或更高版本且來源使用 ``CXX`` 語言時，才會執行"
"掃描。對於屬於 ``CXX_MODULES`` 類型檔案集的來源，始終會執行模組掃描。"
